\id PHP - Ekajuk New Testament
\h Filipai
\toc1 Filipai
\toc2 Fil
\mt2 NWER NYI POL NYONO TV
\mt2 ANEB ERO BA LI GO
\mt1 FILIPAI
\c 1
\nb 
\v 1 Me Pol, a Timoti, wahr ji li alokeltum ba Kraist Jisos, e kpꞌnyono nwer nyia tv aneb Esowo, a atubesi ero, a alokeltum ero ba li go Filipai, ba ma taame tv Kraist Jisos.
\p 
\v 2 Nong, Esowo Nso ejahre, a Ntul a Jisos Kraist ka-n nnoobo, a elkoono.
\s1 Ana Pol jo kak ero ka aneb ero
\p 
\v 3 N kpo kak Esowo ebame saam ngare anyehng anyehng nyi n lꞌbuum-n.\f + \fr 1:3 \ft Rom 1:8\f*
\v 4 Ero abehng abehng bi n kpo kak ka wahn ane kpee, n kpo kak go eyebatahng,
\v 5 a saam akake tib go ebo bi ń jo kak-m go nnoobo etib atiingi bomo ngbokambang efung tete ba rehng lela.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Fil 4:15-16\f*
\v 6 N kpꞌsahb kꞌkahn re, Esowo bi bomo nnoobo eltum alimi go egahne atahng, á bahke gohro lim, gohro song mal efung bio bi Jisos Kraist.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Fil 2:13; 1 Kor 1:4-9\f*
\p 
\v 7 Fꞌfuumu re me n jo tiir-n ana, wahn ane kpee, tibre ń wob-m go eltim. Tibre wahn ebtob bel nnoobo nyi Esowo ana nyi me m ma bel, ń kp-m kake ebo, eji n wob ngbekobo,\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Fil 1:13\f* ń tob kak-m ebo ngare nyi n yiimi nnoobo etib njahm, fere jo nok, eji lꞌyiimi.
\v 8 Esowo bi li ntianse enyame. Ye wo kpꞌkahne elkoro ni ń kp-m koro re me n nyehn-n, elkoro nio ni lohng go eltim ni Kraist Jisos.
\p 
\v 9 N kpꞌkake ero re, elkoro enahne jo gbal na asongo asongo, wahn fere bel elkahne budu, a ngbere,
\v 10 nyi ḿ bahke ma jo liingi nsol nyi ga nob,\f + \fr 1:10 \ft Rom 12:2; Hib 5:13-14\f* eji ń lꞌjol saang, kꞌbel ebi ajehng ajehng efung bio bi Kraist,
\v 11 fere bel akab gbalee, nya lohng go egahne etingitingi elkpin, nya Jisos Kraist kpo wahng kehm kabe, eji Esowo lꞌbel ellub, bo fere jo tehk-e.
\s1 Kraist wo li elkpin ename
\p 
\v 12 Abonanee, n kpꞌsebe re wahn kahn re, jia ji ma-m lim a, ebkak ebo, alum Esowo ebkpe nyange rehng esꞌsong.
\v 13 Abꞌbaabe ba etahk ntubesi, a egom ane bako kpee ebkahn re, n wob ngbekobo tib go esi ji Kraist.\f + \fr 1:13 \ft 2 Tim 2:9\f*
\v 14 Abonanee bandiki gbalee ebbel esahb go eltoono ni bo kpꞌtoono Jisos, tib eji n wob go ngbekobo. Bobkpe bel esahb gbalee budu go alum Esowo abungu, kꞌfahl.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Elt 4:17,29\f*
\p 
\v 15 Etingitingi, ane bandiki kpo bung alum nya Kraist tib eteelala, a ntaange ataange. Wo, ane bandiki kpo bung a ntir atahng nyi nno.
\v 16 Bo ba kpo bung go elkoro. Bo kpꞌkahne re, n wob ana, eji n lꞌyiimi nnoobo etib njahm.
\v 17 Ane bako kpehme bung alum nya Kraist a ntir atahng nyi nno. Bo kpo ra na etul,\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Mak 9:35\f* eji bo lꞌbud-m erem go ngbekobo nyi n wob no.
\p 
\v 18 Jol m-e nehme lub. Atahng kp-m yebe, eji ane kpꞌwuku bada Kraist go mbang anyehng anyehng, afi ane bandiki bungu alum Esowo go mbang awak, afi bo fere bungu go etingitingi.
\v 19 M bahke soro na asi, jo bel eyebatahng. Tibre n kpꞌkahne re, nsol nyia bahke kpiidi, fere jol eltahre ename,\f + \fr 1:19 \ft 2 Kor 4:17\f* tib go egahne ero bi ń kpꞌkake, a ekakebo ji etohko ji Jisos Kraist.
\p 
\v 20 Jo jol-m go eltim gbalee, n fere jo kunu ekpu re, ejum ajehng ajehng kꞌjol ji bahke wahnge bo rik-m ndon, eji n lꞌjol esahb esahb ngare anyehng anyehng, Kraist fere kpe bel na ellub go egama ngubjing, afi n li go elkpin, afi n kpo na.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft 1 Pit 4:16\f*
\v 21 Anv, ejum aji li li elkpin? Egame, elkpin ni n li a ni a, Kraist wo. Afi n kpo na, nsehng nyia.\f + \fr 1:21 \ft 1 Kor 15:55\f*
\v 22 N lꞌjol go elkpin ni ngubjing, n kpꞌkpi eyake ji m bahke ma lim eltum ka Esowo ni kpi nsehng. Owo wahnge n kil kahne ji m bahke yꞌyehke.
\p 
\v 23 Me n sa ayaame mbang. Ji kp-m sahb kꞌkor li re, me n tahm song jol a Kraist. Tibre ano wo ga nob.
\v 24 Tib go egahne esi, ga li re me n jol ana go elkpin.\f + \fr 1:24 \ft Rom 1:11\f*
\v 25 Eji m ma sahb kꞌkahn ano, n kpꞌtob kahn re, m bahke jolo ana go elkpin, fere soro asi a nahne, eji ń lꞌgbal, fere bel eyebatahng go mbang nyi ń kpꞌtoono Esowo.
\v 26 Elgeere ni ḿ bahke geere kak-m go esamahr bi Kraist bahke gbale sehng ngare nyi n lꞌkpe feere ba go egahne.
\s1 Ana e bahke noko ka Kraist
\p 
\v 27 Nong, eljini enahne fuumu a nnoobo etib bi Kraist,\f + \fr 1:27 \ft 1 Tes 2:12\f* eji afi m ba na, ba nyehn-n, afi m maam ba, n lꞌwuk re, wahn baa, yim tꞌtahne go etohko na ajehng, fere kpꞌnoko a eltim anehng ka eltibi ni nnoobo etib bi e kpꞌtaame tv.
\v 28 Kana jo fahl anebekv ebahne go mbang anyehng anyehng.\f + \fr 1:28 \ft Elt 18:9\f* Tibre jia ji bahke tibi ana bo bahke rannge, wahn fere bel eltahre ni lohng goji Esowo.\f + \fr 1:28 \ft 2 Tes 1:4-10\f*
\v 29 Tibre Esowo ebyake eltum ni ḿ bahke jo loko Kraist ka-n, ni li re wahn taame tv-e, fere tob jo nyehn erem tib go ege esi,
\v 30 fere jo nok ebta bꞌnehm bi ń nyehne go egame, a bi ḿ ma wuk anv bada name.\f + \fr 1:30 \ft Elt 28:16-20\f*
\c 2
\s1 Elrede ni Kraist rede elne, a agbal enye
\p 
\v 1 Eji ń kpo rehke atemtem go mbang nyi Kraist, elkoro ene fere jo kak-n eltim, n fere jo jen a Etingi Etohko, fere bel elkoro, a ndon,
\v 2 gohren lim, eji atahng lꞌsahb yeb-m yebe. Belen elkohn ntir atahng nyꞌnehm na anyehng, a elkoro nꞌnehm, a eltim na anehng, wahn fere jol ntir ntir nya anyehng.\f + \fr 2:2 \ft Ef 4:3-6\f*
\v 3 Kana jo ra etul, fere jo geere mbol mbol. Ga nob re, wahn jo rede elnahne, fere jo rod ane bako bum ana ane ba ga nob sehnge wahn.\f + \fr 2:3 \ft Rom 12:10\f*
\v 4 Nong, nne awohng awohng kꞌjo tiiri elne wo wo, á tob jo tiiri ane bako fvfo.\f + \fr 2:4 \ft 1 Kor 10:24,33\f*
\p 
\v 5 Belen ntir atahng ana nyio nyi Kraist Jisos,
\q1 
\v 6 ye ji jolo go ellub ni Esowo.\f + \fr 2:6 \ft Jon 1:2; 17:5\f*
\q1 Á rodem eljolo ni á ma jol jang jang a Esowo bum ana ejum ji bahke jolo ka yefono antahng.
\q1 
\v 7 Á yake ajehng ajehng kpee bum, fere taame, jol nlokeltum, fere ba jol go elfoongo ni nne.\f + \fr 2:7 \ft 2 Kor 8:9\f*
\q1 
\v 8 Eji á jolo nne, á kpe rede elne, fere jo wuk nde tete rehng go elkv, esabsab elkv ni á kpo go ekros.\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Hib 5:8; 12:2\f*
\q1 
\v 9 Owo fvfo, Esowo kehm-e sahb mꞌmehl wahre, fere ka-e mbing nyi gbale sehnge mbing anyehng anyehng,\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Luk 14:7-11\f*
\q1 
\v 10 eji nne awohng awohng no li ejahbetul Esowo, a njini, a atahng ndi lꞌjamme alahng enye, fere jo kak mbing nyi Jisos,
\q1 
\v 11 fere jo bung go ege a nnyo re, Jisos Kraist wo li Ntul, fere jo ka Esowo Nsoo ellub.\f + \fr 2:11 \ft Ell 5:13\f*
\s1 Jo yaan ana atꞌrekahng go njini
\p 
\v 12 Akpondahme enyame, ana ń jo wuk-m ngare anyehng anyehng eji n jolo a nahne, anv, eji n ki kpe li a nahne wo ga nob re, wahn jo ga-m wuk. Noken go elfahle, a akahb akahme, eji ń lꞌgohro bel eltahre enahne.\f + \fr 2:12 \ft 1 Pit 1:17\f*
\v 13 Tibre Esowo kpi nlimi nlimi eltum go egahne atahng, eji mbang enye lꞌjo kor-n, ń fere jo wuk-e, fere jo lim ji á kpꞌsebe re wahn lim.\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Jon 15:5; 2 Kor 3:5\f*
\p 
\v 14 Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌjo lim, kana jo lim go elmemme, a nfaabe alimi,
\v 15 eji ń lꞌjol saang, nnene ki-n ka ebi, wahn fere jol abon Esowo ba ki kpi elem ajehng ajehng eji ń lene go njini nyi ma bvvrv, fere gbal abꞌbi abꞌbi. Jo yaan ana atꞌrekahng go njini nyia,\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Mat 5:14; Ef 5:8\f*
\v 16 wahn fere jabbe alum nya elkpin tꞌtahne, eji n lꞌjo geere efung bio bi Kraist, ana nne no ki be abahl mbol mbol, fere bade, jo lim eltum mbol mbol.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft 1 Tes 3:5\f*
\v 17 Lꞌfere jol re bo bahk-m rodo, yaange ana alahb njom wohng go ejum njom,\f + \fr 2:17 \ft 2 Tim 4:6\f* ji li elloko ni ń kpꞌloko Esowo bi ḿ ma taame tv-e, n kpꞌgeere, fere bel eyebatahng a nahne.
\v 18 Ano wo fvfo ḿ bahke tob bel eyebatahng, fere tob-m elgeere.
\s1 Timoti abola Epafroditus
\p 
\v 19 N kpꞌbumu Ntul a Jisos go etingitingi re m bahke gulu eltumu Timoti tv-n, eji n lꞌwuk bade ana ń li no, fere rede av.
\p 
\v 20 Nnene n kpeem kpi ana ye, no kpo sahb tiir-n tiiri.
\v 21 Ane bako kpee kpo ga kunu ekpu go bo a nsol. Bo kpehme ga kunu ekpu go nsol nyi Jisos Kraist.\f + \fr 2:21 \ft 2 Tim 4:16\f*
\v 22 Wo Timoti, ń kp-e kahne re, á kpꞌtibi eljini ni nno. Ń kpꞌkahne ana á ma jol ana mmon ewame no bo jo kod abo ano abola nde, jo loko Esowo eji e jo tiingi nnoobo etib.\f + \fr 2:22 \ft 1 Tim 1:2\f*
\v 23 N kpꞌbumu re me n tum-e, n lꞌsoro kꞌkahn ji bahke jolo a name.
\p 
\v 24 N kpꞌbumu Jehova go etingitingi re, mefono bahke tob gulu elbake.\f + \fr 2:24 \ft Fil 1:25\f*
\v 25 N tiri re, nꞌnob re me n tum mmonanne Epafroditus tv-n, ye ji e kpꞌlimi eltum a ne ano. Á tob li nne a nsoja no Kraist ana me. Ye wo li nne no ń tum-e re, á ba kak-m ebo.\f + \fr 2:25 \ft Fil 4:18\f*
\v 26 Á kpꞌsahb sꞌseb re á nyehn-n wahn ane kpee. Ndon gbal-e go eltim sehng tib eji ń wuku re, á jo yꞌyam.
\v 27 Etingitingi, á yame sehng, jol kehn á kpo. Á fili Esowo ndon, jol ye ye sang, me fvfo, eji n lꞌkꞌjo jol ndon ndon.
\p 
\v 28 Owo wahnge sahb li-m li re me n tum-e, eji ń lꞌkpe-e nyehn, fere bel eyebatahng, kꞌkpe ga jol ndon ndon.
\v 29 Koon ye go eyebatahng ana nne no Jehova tumu no. Jo kaken elkohn ane ana bao.
\v 30 Tibre sa ntiil á kpo, tib go eltum ni Kraist. Á taame elkv, eji á lꞌgohr-m loko eltum ni ń kil-m elkpe ma loko, tib eji ń li fee.\f + \fr 2:30 \ft Fai 13\f*
\c 3
\s1 Ana Pol bungu bade elne
\p 
\v 1 Abonanee, ji n yahke gohro bung li re, wahn bel eyebatahng go ejang bi Jehova. M-e nehme kpen re me n jo nyon nsol nyꞌnehm tv-n. Tibre nya nya bahk-n limi, ń lohko kahn.
\p 
\v 2 Jo gberen ebv,\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Mat 7:6\f* wahn fere jo gbere abꞌbi abalimeltum, a ane ba kpo fang agubjing ebo alok.\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Gal 2:12\f*
\v 3 Tibre wahr ba li ane ba ma yehke etingitingi nrur, wahr ji kpꞌkake Esowo go etohko,\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Jon 4:24\f* fere jo geere kak Kraist Jisos. Wahr kpehme bum re, Esowo bahke koko nne tib go nsol nyi á limi go ege a ngubjing.
\v 4 Fvfo, nsol nyia, nyi kehn jol tob wahng n tob tir ano. Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtir re, Esowo bahk-e koko tib go nsol nyi li ka ngubjing, me wo ga kpi sehng-e.
\v 5 Bo yehk-m nrur, eji m ma kang nfung enehkeni. Me nne Israel wo. N lohng go etꞌtohngo ji Benjamin. Me nne a Hibru wo dahb dahb dahb. Babnsoo, anebe Hibru ba. Bade eyaame ji atahm abumu, me nne a Farisi wo.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Elt 26:5\f*
\v 6 N jo kake ekpuku go eltum Esowo, eji n jo nohk aneb ero. Bade eyaame ji nne bahke lehke eno go esamahr bi Esowo tib eji á kpi atahm bum, n jolo nne no bo ki-m jo ma ka ebi ajehng ajehng.
\p 
\v 7 Nsol nyi n jo tir re m bahke lehke nsehng, me n fere rod bum ana nsol nyi ki lohng ejumjum tib go esi ji Kraist.
\v 8 Etingitingi, n kpꞌrodo ejum ajehng ajehng ana ejum ji ki lohng ejumjum tib go elkahne ni n kpꞌkahne Kraist Jisos Ntul ewame, ni ga gbal sehnge ejum ajehng ajehng. Esi eje ji wahnge m ma ro ejum ajehng ajehng go, fere rod bum ana nkahr, eji n lꞌli nsehng nyio nyi li Kraist,\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Mat 19:27-29\f*
\v 9 fere jol ajehng a ne, kꞌjol nne no ma li eno jꞌje antahng. Anv, me n li eno go esamahr Esowo, ji nne bahke lehke á lꞌtaame tv Kraist, elkohn eno ji kpo lohng goji Esowo, ji ane ba kpꞌtaame tv-e bahke lehke,\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Rom 3:20-22\f*
\v 10 eji n lꞌkahn Kraist, fere kahn nsahm nyi nyahm-e go elkv,\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Rom 6:5-6\f* fere tob nyehn erem ebe, fere tob jol ana ye go ege elkv ni á kpo no,\f + \fr 3:10 \ft 2 Kor 4:10\f*
\v 11 eji limi limi kan, n lꞌtob nyahme go elkv.
\p 
\v 12 Lohngem re me n si bꞌbel.\f + \fr 3:12 \ft 1 Jon 3:2\f* Lohngem re me n si jꞌjol go nseenga nseenge. N kpꞌsoro asi, jo nyennge, eji lꞌjol jꞌjame. Tibre Kraist ma-m ko, lim jꞌje.
\p 
\v 13 Abonanee, n nehme rod elname bum ana nne no ma lohko bel. Fvfo, ejum ajehng jia, ji n kpꞌlimi. Me n yini ekpu go nsol nyi wuku wuku n jo lim. Me n tanne abahl fi re me n song bel nsol nyi li go esꞌsong.
\v 14 Ano wo wahnge n kpꞌbeke asongo go edi ji bo tibi tv, eji n lꞌbel eltuuru ni li elkpin ni e bahke bele go ero, ni wahnge Esowo lung-r no, ni li goji Kraist Jisos.
\s1 Leemen eljini ename
\p 
\v 15 Nong, ane kpee ba li go nseenga nseenge bel ntir nyia.\f + \fr 3:15 \ft 1 Kor 2:6\f* Ń lꞌfere tir ntir nyindikandiki, Esowo bahke tob lennge ejum jia ka-n.
\v 16 Afi jolo elkohn ejum aji, nong, wahr soren asi, jo toono mbang nyi wuku wuku e bomo eltoono tete ba rehng anv.\f + \fr 3:16 \ft Gal 6:16\f*
\p 
\v 17 Abonanee, leemen eljini ename, wahn jo kunu ane ba kpꞌtob jen ano ekpu, jang jang ana e ma-n tib mbang nyi ḿ bahke jo toono.\f + \fr 3:17 \ft 1 Kor 11:1\f*
\p 
\v 18 M ma-n tohko tong nkpel a nkpele, anv, n kp-n kpeke tong a abonngo go amahr re, ane gbalee kpꞌjene ana anebekv bao ba ekros ji Kraist.
\v 19 Esꞌkohlo ebo bahke jolo elrannge. Nsol alehke ebo nyi li Esowo ebo.\f + \fr 3:19 \ft Rom 16:18\f* Nsol nyi kehn jol jo fili bo ndon, nyi nyi bo kpꞌfere geere kak. Bobyehke ekunukpu ebo, kunu go nsol nyi njini nyia.
\p 
\v 20 Wahr ba li afono ejahbetul Esowo, edi jio ji Ntul a Jisos Kraist ntꞌtahre ewahre bahke lohngo ba, ye jio ji e kp-e siki,\f + \fr 3:20 \ft Hib 11:10\f*
\v 21 ye ji bahke koko nsahm enye yaange agubjing enyahre nya li rede rede, fere jol ana ngubjing enye nyi kpi ellub.\f + \fr 3:21 \ft 1 Kor 15:51\f* Nsahm enye nyi bahke wahnge á mal lim nsol kpee woom-e go elwo.
\c 4
\s1 Esꞌkohro erehke
\p 
\v 1 Fvfo, abonanee, wahn ji kpo kor-m, wahn ba n jo seb re me n nyehn-n, wahn ba li eyebatahng ejame, a ekpasi etul ejame. Akpondahme enyame, yiimen tꞌtahne go mbang nyi Ntul.
\p 
\v 2 N kpꞌrehke Eyodia, a Sintike re bo jol go ntir anyehng ana abonanyehn nne go ejang bi Esowo.
\p 
\v 3 Sisigus, nkakesehk a nte ewame, n kp-a gboongo re, wo lub kak bo ebo. Tibre bo jo noko, jo tob-m eltum nio ni nnoobo etib, a Klement fvfo, a ane bako ba e jo tob lim eltum ano a bo, ba abing ebo wob go nwer nyi elkpin.\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Luk 10:20; Ell 20:15\f*
\v 4 Jo belen eyebatahng ngare anyehng anyehng, tib eji ń li ajehng a Jehova. N kpꞌkpeke bung re wahn bel eyebatahng.
\v 5 Nong, nne awohng awohng kahn nnaange eljini enahne. Tibre Ntul a Jisos ebkabbe kpidi kpidi.
\v 6 Kana jo tiiri ejum ajehng ajehng.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Mat 6:25-34\f* Ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń lꞌkehm sebe, jo limen Esowo, á kahn, eji ń kpꞌkake ero, fere jo gboong-e a saam akake.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft 1 Pit 5:7\f*
\p 
\v 7 Ń lꞌlim ano, owo elkoono ni Esowo ni gbale sehnge elkahne anehng anehng bahke jo baabe ntim enyahne, a ntir atahng enyahne, eji ń li ajehng a Kraist Jisos.\f + \fr 4:7 \ft Jon 14:27; Kol 3:15\f*
\p 
\v 8 Abonanee, alum nya a, nya ma-m gohro sa, nya m bahke gohro bung. Jo tiren bade ejum ajehng ajehng ji li go etingitingi, ji kpi ekpunu, ji li nseenge, ji li saang, ji kpi ano, ji kpi elgahm ni nno, ji kpꞌnobo, a ji ane kpo tehk.
\p 
\v 9 Jo limen ejum ajehng ajehng ji ń kpili go egame, a ji ḿ bele go egame. Jo limen ajehng ajehng ji ḿ ma wuk, fere nyehn go egame. Owo Esowo bi elkoono bahke jolo a nahne.
\s1 Ana Pol kake anebe Filipai saam
\p 
\v 10 Eltim kp-m yebe gbalee go ejang bi Jehova. Tib eji ma kang gbalee, anv, ma-n kpe melle re wahn jo tiir-m. Jia lohngem re, me ń kpeem jo tiiri, sehngem eyake ji ń ki bel.
\p 
\v 11 N nehme bung alum nyaa tib eji nsol ma-m lehng. N kpili re, afi n jolo elkohn ani, ebnob a name.\f + \fr 4:11 \ft 1 Tim 6:6\f*
\v 12 N kpꞌkahne ana kpo jol, nsol lꞌlehng-m, fere kahn ana kpo jol, n lꞌbel gbalee. Me n kpili re, ejum ajehng ajehng ebnob a name, afi n wohngo na, afi n li a njal, afi m bele gbalee, afi lehng-m na.
\v 13 M bahke ma yiimi go elkohn ejum ajehng ajehng ji lꞌba a name, tibre Kraist wo kpo kak-m eko.\f + \fr 4:13 \ft 2 Kor 12:10\f*
\p 
\v 14 Ń limi nob nob, eji ń kak-m ebo go egame afemfem.
\v 15 Wahn anebe Filipai, wahnfono antahng kpꞌkahne re, go mbomannahb, eji m bomo nnoobo etib go eltiingi, ngare nyi n tahme o Masedonia, ero abehng abehng jolem bi tob ka-m ejum ana bo bele go egame, sehngem wahn ba ba ka-m no.\f + \fr 4:15 \ft 2 Kor 11:9\f*
\p 
\v 16 Eji n jolo go Tesalonaika, ń tumu akpohko tv-m, ń kpe bulu, kpe tum tv-m, jo kak-m ebo.
\p 
\v 17 Lohngem re ayare nya n kpꞌsebe. N kpꞌsebe re me n nyehn akab, eji eltuuru enahne lꞌkpe gbal budu.
\p 
\v 18 Me m bel nsol kpee, nsol ma-m tv. Ejumjum limm, ji ma-m kpe rin, eji Epafroditus ma ko ayare nya ń tumu no tv-m ba ka-m,\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Fil 2:25\f* nya li ana ayare nya kpo v Esowo eleenge, nya li ana ejum njom ji kpo kor Esowo, á fere ko.
\p 
\v 19 Esowo ebame bi kpi afang go ege ellub, nya li goji Kraist Jisos bahk-n kake ejum ajehng ajehng ji ma-n rin.
\v 20 Nong, ellub jol ka Esowo Nso ejahre go njinanjini. Emen.
\s1 Nnyo akake
\p 
\v 21 Kaken nne Esowo awohng awohng nnyo, no li ka Kraist Jisos.
\p Abonanee ba li a name kp-n tob kak nnyo.
\v 22 Aneb Esowo kpee kp-n kake nnyo, asehngesehnge ane ba li go etahk ntul a Rom.
\p 
\v 23 Nong, nnoobo nyi Ntul a Jisos Kraist jol a atohko enyahne, wahn ane kpee.
